\mt1 Matiu
\mt2 Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r R…ôha Iesu Kristo It…ôm Matiu T…ôm…ôte
\imt1 N…ôghat…ôn …ôku…ôk…®r r…ôha naoa u Matiu
\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Matiu t…ôm…ôte naoa u. In et…ôm tuelef kit r…ôha Iesu. N…ôrg…®n kit m…®n u Lifae. Matiu in et…ôm Isrel it…ôm tatos m…ôni r…ôha takis r…ôha kapman r…ôha Rom. M…ôto Iesu t…ômaun-in m…ôm…ô in otuwa r…ôhan kit et…ômim.
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* T…ôm…ôte naoa u tatuw…®n o net…ôm Isrel, m…ôto t…ôm…ôte e n…ôghat…ôn Kris it…ôm tahmen …ôm e Bislama r…ôha net…ôm m…®n rafin ik…®n …ôh.
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Naoa u tat…®lp…®n Oltesteman ne Niutesteman m…ôto-inu in tat…ôghat-in tep…ôt e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha ien m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n aup…ôn it…ôm k…ôm…ôte e Oltesteman. E nian r…ôha Iesu, net…ôm Isrel k…ômoatat…®g ahgin kapman r…ôha Rom. K…ômoat…ôsahgin suah kit it…ôm otuwa mosmeg…ôh ilat. Koataun-in suah u m…ôm…ô Kristo, o Mesaea.
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Matiu t…ôm…ôte naoa u m…ôm…ô ot…ôn-iar…ôp w…®r m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kristo (Mesaea), et…ôm it…ôm Uhg…®n t…®n…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô ot…ôpanahl-ipa m…ôm…ô otuwa mosmeg…ôh Isrel. Matiu t…ôm…ôghat-in n…ôghat…ôn tep…ôt r…ôha Uhg…®n e Oltesteman it…ôm ien m…®n kot…ôghat-in Iesu, k…ôn mat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u kotiet-pa e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Iesu. K…ôn Matiu tolkeike m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…®tun m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kig it…ôm in il…®s e kig m…®n rafin.
\c 1
\s1 T…®p…® Iesu Kristo rat m…®n
\r (Luk 3:23‚Äì38)
\m 
\v 1 Inu n…ôrg…® t…®p…® Iesu Kristo rat m…®n, kit in Kig Tef…®t, k…ôn kit m…®n in Epraham.\x - \xo 1:1 \xt Jen 22:18; 1 Kron 17:11\x*
\li1 
\v 2 Epraham in tata r…ôha Aisak,
\li2 k…ôn Aisak in tata r…ôha Jekop,
\li2 k…ôn Jekop in tata r…ôha Juta ne pian m…®n,
\li2 
\v 3 k…ôn Juta in tata r…ôha Peres ne Sera, r…ôhalau mama u Temar,
\li2 k…ôn Peres in tata r…ôha Hesron,
\li2 k…ôn Hesron in tata r…ôha Ram,\x - \xo 1:3 \xt Jen 38:29‚Äì30; Rut 4:18-22\x*
\li2 
\v 4 k…ôn Ram in tata r…ôha Aminatap,
\li2 k…ôn Aminatap in tata r…ôha Nason,
\li2 k…ôn Nason in tata r…ôha Salmon,
\li2 
\v 5 k…ôn Salmon in tata r…ôha Poas u r…ôhan mama Rehap,
\li2 k…ôn Poas in tata r…ôha Opet u r…ôhan mama u Rut,
\li2 k…ôn Opet in tata r…ôha Jese,\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Rut 4:13-17\x*
\li2 
\v 6 k…ôn Jese in tata r…ôha Kig Tef…®t.\x - \xo 1:6 \xt 2 Saml 12:24\x*
\li1 K…ôn Kig Tef…®t in tata r…ôha Solomon u r…ôhan mama in p…ôtan r…ôha Uria aup…ôn,
\li2 
\v 7 k…ôn Solomon in tata r…ôha Rehopoam,
\li2 k…ôn Rehopoam in tata r…ôha Apia,
\li2 k…ôn Apia in tata r…ôha Asa,
\li2 
\v 8 k…ôn Asa in tata r…ôha Jehosafat,
\li2 k…ôn Jehosafat in tata r…ôha Jehoram,
\li2 k…ôn Jehoram in pipi rat r…ôha Usia,
\li2 
\v 9 k…ôn Usia in tata r…ôha Jotam,
\li2 k…ôn Jotam in tata r…ôha Ahas,
\li2 k…ôn Ahas in tata r…ôha Hesekia,
\li2 
\v 10 k…ôn Hesekia in tata r…ôha Manase,
\li2 k…ôn Manase in tata r…ôha Amon,
\li2 k…ôn Amon in tata r…ôha Josaea,
\li2 
\v 11 k…ôn Josaea in tata r…ôha Jekonaea ne pian m…®n, k…ôn uaris…®g lan, t…®k…®m…®r m…®n r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômot…ôm…®k ilat motuw…®n Papilon m…ôm…ô ilat okotuwa slef m…®n r…ôhalat.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt 2 King 22‚Äî24; 2 Kron 36:10; Jer 27:20\x*
\li1 
\v 12 K…ôn inu n…ôrg…® pipi m…®n it…ôm t…ôm…ôtuoun e nian noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômotuw…®n Papilon.
\li2 Jekonaea in tata r…ôha Sealtiel,
\li2 k…ôn Sealtiel in pipi r…ôha Serupapel,\x - \xo 1:12 \xt Esra 3:2\x*
\li2 
\v 13 k…ôn Serupapel in tata r…ôha Apiut,
\li2 k…ôn Apiut in tata r…ôha Eliakim,
\li2 k…ôn Eliakim in tata r…ôha Asor,
\li2 
\v 14 k…ôn Asor in tata r…ôha Satok,
\li2 k…ôn Satok in tata r…ôha Akim,
\li2 k…ôn Akim in tata r…ôha Eliut,
\li2 
\v 15 k…ôn Eliut, in tata r…ôha Eleasar,
\li2 k…ôn Eleasar in tata r…ôha Matan,
\li2 k…ôn Matan in tata r…ôha Jekop,
\li2 
\v 16 k…ôn Jekop in tata r…ôha Josep u i…ôrman r…ôha Meri.
\li2 K…ôn Meri t…ôm…®l…ôs Iesu, k…ôn k…ôtaun-in m…ôm…ô Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa.
\p 
\v 17 T…ôm…ôtuoun e Epraham m…ôtoarus-p…ôn Kig Tef…®t, pipi rat m…®n …ôm u neen k…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s n…ôrg…®lat, ilat fotin. K…ôn t…ôm…ôtuoun m…®n e Kig Tef…®t m…ôtoarus-p…ôn noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômotuw…®n Papilon, pipi rat m…®n ilat rafin fotin. K…ôn t…ôm…ôtuoun m…®n e noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômotuw…®n Papilon m…ôtoarus-p…ôn Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa, pipi rat m…®n ilat rafin fotin.
\s1 Naiir…ôn r…ôha Iesu Kristo
\r (Luk 2:1-7)
\p 
\v 18 Inu namnus…ôn r…ôha naiir…ôn r…ôha Iesu Kristo. Mama r…ôha Iesu, n…ôrg…®n u Meri, k…®n…ôn r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô okos r…ôhan k…ôt…®m kan m…ôm…ô ot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn suah kit, n…ôrg…®n u Josep. M…ôto e nian k…ôsueam…ôn …ôh muat…®g kiti…ôh, k…ôn Josep t…ôsuw…®n…ôn …ôh mehm, m…ôto Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…®nol m…ôm…ô Meri t…®n…ôp…ôk-…ôp…ôk r…ôk…®s.\x - \xo 1:18 \xt Luk 1:27,35\x*
\v 19 K…ôn r…ôhan iagu…®hl Josep in et…ôm …ôtuat…®p, k…ôn tat…ôt…ôl…®g-in m…ôm…ô otap…ôs Meri, m…ôto in t…ôsolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô otol Meri taul…®s, k…ôn n…®kin t…ôht m…ôm…ô ot…ôs…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn k…ôm net…ômim.
\p 
\v 20 M…ôto nian n…®kin t…ômat…ôht m…ôm…ô in otol n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn …ôh, k…ôn nagelo kit r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômuwa ron e nap…®laiir…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúJosep, mip…® Tef…®t rat. On…ôk…ôs…ôg…®n…ôn m…ôm…ô onakit Meri m…ôm…ô in r…ôham p…ôtan, m…ôto-inu suak…ôku …ôh t…ôtat…®g lan, in t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn …ôm o Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n.
\v 21 K…ôn in ot…®l…ôs n…ôt…®n kit i…ôrman, k…ôn on…ôkaun-in n…ôrg…®n m…ôm…ô Iesu m…ôto-inu in otosmeg…ôh r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim e nol…ôn t…ôrat m…®n r…ôhalat.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:21 \ft Iesu, n…®p…ôt…® tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô tatosmeg…ôh‚Äù \f* \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Luk 1:31; 2:21\x*
\v 22 Nat…®mnat m…®n rafin …ôh k…ômotuwa kol …ôm n…®pahrien…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô it…ôm r…ôhan kit ien t…ôm…ôn aup…ôn ik…®n m…ôm…ô,
\v 23 ‚ÄúP…ôtan …ôk…ôku kit it…ôm i…ôrman t…ôsuw…®n…ôn …ôh ron, ot…ôp…ôs m…ôw…®g, k…ôn pan…®l…ôs n…ôt…®n kit i…ôrman, k…ôn okaun-in n…ôrg…®n m…ôm…ô Emanuel,‚Äù\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Aes 7:14\x* inu n…®p…ôt…®n t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúUhg…®n t…ôtat…®g kitat min.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 K…ôn nian Josep t…ômaiir, k…ôn t…ôm…ôt…ôu-p…ôn …ôm n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha nagelo r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. K…ôn t…ômuw…®n mit Meri muwa e r…ôhan latu…ônu m…ôm…ô r…ôhan p…ôtan,
\v 25 m…ôto in t…ôm…ôsuw…®n…ôn …ôh mehm matuw…®n matuw…®n m…ôtoarus-p…ôn Meri t…®l…ôs n…ôt…®n i…ôrman. K…ôn Josep t…ômaun-in n…ôrg…®n m…ôm…ô Iesu.\x - \xo 1:25 \xt Luk 2:21\x*
\c 2
\s1 Net…ôm-iasol k…ômotairahgin Iesu
\m 
\v 1 Iesu t…ômaiir …ôp…ôh n…®t…ôn r…ôha Jutia e taon Petlehem e nian Kig Herot Asol in t…ômat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô lan. K…ôn uaris…®g ik…®n, net…ôm-iasol m…®n neen k…ômot…®s…®-par is…ôu motuwa Jerusalem. Kotenat…®g w…®r e n…ôn…ôn n…®p…ôt…® m…ôhau m…®n. K…ôn motuwa mot…ôtap…ôh m…ôm…ô,
\v 2 ‚Äú?Suak…ôku u in hi…ô, it…ôm in t…ômaiir m…ôm…ô in kig r…ôha net…ôm Isrel? Emotehm r…ôhan m…ôhau t…ôm…ôr …ôp…ôh par, k…ôn ekoatuwa m…ôm…ô ekotos-ip…ôn n…®siaii…ôn k…ôm in.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:2 \xt Nam 24:17\x*
\p 
\v 3 Nian Kig Herot Asol t…ôm…ôto n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, ilat net…ôm Jerusalem n…®kilat rafin t…ôm…ôrat.
\v 4 K…ôn t…ômarg…ôf…®m…®n pris asol m…®n ne i…ôg…ôtun m…®n r…ôha Lou r…ôha n…ôfak…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, k…ôn mat…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú?Kristo it…ôm Uhg…®n t…®n…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa, in otaiir hi…ô?‚Äù
\v 5 K…ôn k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIn otaiir …ôp…ôh taon Petlehem e n…®t…ôn r…ôha Jutia. M…ôto-inu ien kit r…ôha Uhg…®n aup…ôn, t…ôm…ôte tol min-nulan m…ôm…ô,
\v 6 ‚ÄòIk Petlehem …ôp…ôh e n…®t…ôn Juta, okol k…ôs…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô ik nat …ôpnap…®n e net…ôm-iasol m…®n …ôp…ôh ik…®n Juta, m…ôto-inu et…ôm-iasol kit ot…®s…®-p…ôn lam, k…ôn in otatehm w…®r r…ôhak m…®n net…ôm Isrel tahmen-p…ôn e et…ôm tatehm w…®r r…ôhan sipsip m…®n.‚Äô‚Äù\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Maeka 5:2; Jon 7:42\x*
\p 
\v 7 K…ôn Kig Herot Asol t…ômaun-in net…ôm kotenat…®g w…®r e n…ôn…ôn n…®p…ôt…® m…ôhau m…®n kotuwa tu…ôf…®m…®n anion ilat, mat…ôtap…ôh olat m…ôm…ô m…ôhau …ôh t…ôm…ôr …ôtuat…®p e nian naka, k…ôn k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn nian r…ôha m…ôhau k…ôm in.
\v 8 K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOtuw…®n Petlehem moteg…ôs-in w…®r suak…ôku. Nian on…ôkotehm un, k…ôn nakotos n…ôghat…ôn lan motuwa m…ôm…ô io m…®n ekuw…®n mos-ip…ôn n…®siaii…ôn k…ôm in.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9-10 Nian k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, k…ômotiet motuw…®n, k…ôn motehm m…ôhau ilouin it…ôm k…ômotehm …ôp…ôh par. Nian k…ômotehm m…®n m…ôhau …ôh, n…®kilat t…ômagien t…ômagien. K…ôn m…ôhau un t…ômaup…ôn-in ilat muw…®n mat…ôtul …ôtuat…®p …ôh suak…ôku ilouin t…ôtap…®l ik…®n.\fig |alt="Three wise men offering gifts to Jesus" src="LB00295B.TIF" size="col" loc="Mat 2:9-12" ref="Mat 2:9-10"\fig*
\v 11 K…ôn k…ômotuw…®n …ôh im…ô, motehm suak…ôku ilau r…ôhan mama Meri. K…ôn k…ômot…®sin nul…®lat moatos-ip…ôn n…®siaii…ôn k…ôm suak…ôku …ôh. K…ôn k…ômotiel…®g naut…ô e r…ôhalat k…ôt…®m m…®n it…ôm n…ômt…®lat ti…ôk…®s, moatos-ip…ôn k…ôm in. K…ômoatos-ip…ôn iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t, ne nat kit m…®n it…ôm n…ômi…ôw…®n t…ôw…®r nian katuwan e n…®g…ôm, n…ôrg…®n u frankinsens, ne fomat it…ôm n…ômi…ôw…®n t…ôw…®r, n…ôrg…®n u m…®r.\x - \xo 2:11 \xt Sam 72:10-15; Aes 60:6\x*
\p 
\v 12 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôhau ilat e nap…®laiir…ôn m…ôm…ô ok…ôsot…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn…ôn o Kig Herot Asol. K…ôn in…ôh ilat k…ômotaw…®l…ôk-in Kig Herot motuw…®n-p…ôn e suat…®p p…®s…®n moatuw…®n im…ôlat ik…®n.
\s1 Josep ne Meri k…ômial…ôs Iesu m…ôhlag…®m m…ôhaluw…®n …ôp…ôh Ijip
\p 
\v 13 Nian net…ôm kotenat…®g w…®r m…®n u k…ômotiet r…ôk…®s m…®noatuw…®n, k…ôn nagelo kit r…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômuwa miet-ar…ôpa o Josep e nap…®laiir…ôn mat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆ètul u…ôhai, m…®l…ôs suak…ôku ilau r…ôhan mama, on…ôk…ôhlag…®m m…ôhaluw…®n …ôp…ôh Ijip. K…ôn onat…ôhlat…®g …ôh-ik…®n m…ôtoarus-p…ôn io …ôm ek…ôn-ip…®n…ô m…®n k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô on…ôk…ôhal…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n, m…ôto-inu ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, Kig Herot Asol team-in suak…ôku u m…ôm…ô otohamnu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 K…ôn …ômun e nian …ôh lap…®n, Josep t…ôm…ôtul m…®l…ôs suak…ôku ilau r…ôhan mama m…ôhlag…®m m…ôt…ôhaluw…®n …ôp…ôh Ijip.
\v 15 K…ôn k…ôm…ôt…ôhlat…®g e n…®m…ôpt…ôn …ôh m…ôtoarus-p…ôn Kig Herot Asol ot…®m…®s. Nat u t…®nuwa m…ôm…ô otol n…®pahrien…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s aup…ôn e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha ien kit tat…ôn min-nulan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúEmaun-in n…ôt…®k i…ôrman m…ôm…ô otiet r…ôk…®s Ijip.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:15 \xt Hos 11:1\x*
\s1 Mopael m…®n r…ôha Kig Herot Asol k…ômotohamnu n…®sualk…ôl…ôh n…ôman
\p 
\v 16 K…ôn e nian Kig Herot Asol t…ôm…®tun m…ôm…ô net…ôm kotenat…®g w…®r e m…ôhau m…®n k…ôm…ôsotol…ôn n…ôwian motaw…®l…ôk-in motag…®m, k…ôn n…®kin t…ômahm…ô p…®k ag…®n. K…ôn in t…ômahl-ip…ôn r…ôhan mopael m…®n m…ôm…ô okotuw…®n Petlehem ne ik…®n m…®n rafin t…®t…ôlau lan, m…ôm…ô okoteam-in n…®sualk…ôl…ôh i…ôrman m…®n it…ôm r…ôhalat nup t…ôsapr…ôk…®s-in…ôn nup k…ôiu, k…ôn okotohamnu ilat rafin. In t…ôm…®t…ôpun nup k…ôiu n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu n…®kin t…ôm…ôht m…ôm…ô nian …ôtuat…®p …ôh it…ôm net…ôm kotenat…®g k…ômotehm m…ôhau lan.
\v 17 Nat…®mnat m…®n u t…ômol n…ôghat…ôn u tuwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn lan it…ôm ien Jeremaea t…®n…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s aup…ôn ik…®n m…ôm…ô,
\v 18 ‚ÄúNet…ôm Rama k…ômot…ôto p…ôtan kit t…ôtas…ôk t…ôtas…ôk m…ôto-inu tat…ôto t…ôrat ag…®n. P…ôtan …ôh in Rejel, in t…ôtas…ôk o r…ôhan n…®sualk…ôl…ôh. K…ôn m…ôsolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô suah kit otuwa m…ôghat m…®l…ôs-ip…ôr m…®n r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…ôto-inu r…ôhan m…®n n…®sualk…ôl…ôh k…®not…®m…®s rafin.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:18 \xt Jer 31:15\x*\f + \fr 2:18 \ft E ves u, n…ôrg…®n u Retiel, tat…ôtul o mama m…®n rafin r…ôha Isrel.\f*
\s1 Josep ne Meri ne suak…ôku k…ôm…ôhaliet Ijip m…ôhal…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn Nasaret
\p 
\v 19 Uaris…®g e nian Kig Herot Asol t…ôm…®m…®s, m…ôto Josep ne Meri ne suak…ôku kat…ôhlat…®g …ôh …ôp…ôh Ijip, k…ôn nagelo kit r…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômuwa o Josep e nap…®laiir…ôn kit mat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô,
\v 20 ‚ÄúJosep. ∆ètul m…®l…ôs suak…ôku ne r…ôhan mama k…ôn m…ôhal…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn e n…ôpt…ôn …ôh Isrel, m…ôto-inu net…ôm m…®n u k…ômotolkeike m…ôm…ô okotohamnu suak…ôku, ilat k…®not…®m…®s r…ôk…®s.‚Äù
\v 21 K…ôn Josep t…ôm…ôtul m…®l…ôs suak…ôku …ôh ne r…ôhan mama, k…ôn m…ôhal…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn m…®n e n…ôpt…ôn …ôh Isrel.
\p 
\v 22 M…ôto nian Josep t…ôm…ôto m…ôm…ô Akeleas t…ômos n…ôme r…ôhan tata Kig Herot Asol mat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e Jutia, k…ôn in t…ôm…ôgin n…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn…ôn Jutia. K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôghat k…ôm Josep e nap…®laiir…ôn kit m…®n m…ôm…ô in ot…ôsuw…®n…ôn Jutia, k…ôn t…ômiet muw…®n ik…®n p…®s…®n e n…®t…ôn asol Kalili.
\v 23 K…ôn k…ôm…ôhaluw…®n m…ôt…ôhlat…®g n…®t…ôn …ôh Kalili e taon kit, n…ôrg…®n u Nasaret, m…ôm…ô otol n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha ien m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n aup…ôn otuwa mol n…®pahrien…ôn. Ilat k…ômot…ôn-ip…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOkot…ôn m…ôm…ô in et…ôm Nasaret.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:23 \xt Aes 11:1; 53:2; Luk 2:39; Jon 1:45\x*
\c 3
\s1 Jon Baptais t…ôtamnus-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n
\r (Mak 1:1-8; Luk 3:1-9, 15-17; // Jon 1:19-28)
\m 
